item.title: Moparisthebest in need help from u!
item.dc:creator: @PaulT PaulT
item.description:
@PaulT wrote:

Download the newest version here. It uses a standard installer instead of rar archiving. Which is more noob friendly :).

On the other hand, extracting an RAR and then opening runmoparscape.bat is pretty easy as well. You simply click “Extract to” then browse to the folder where you extracted the game files. Then open runmoparscape.bat

I have the latest JDK and I made them open as archives because it’s much more convenient.
